<strong>How can I keep in touch with the Roots of Empathy organization and find out more about Roots of Empathy programs and Seeds of Empathy programs?</strong><br>
If you’d like to receive our Roots of Empathy newsletter Green Blanket, and an occasional update on our news and plans for expansion, please fill in our <a href="https://app.etapestry.com/onlineforms/RootsofEmpathy/mailing.html">online registration form</a>.</p>
<p>Thank you for your interest in the Roots of Empathy organization.</p>
